{"tid":357223,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有個撚樣扮日本人既騙子比我怒屌","createTime":"2017-08-12T16:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T16:56:03.000Z","uid":57952,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b48e112546e547f00b89fa34a2008448edec57a6","tid":357223,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"話說今日三點鐘左右起旺角 朗豪坊對出 <br />\n有個帶眼鏡 大概三十歲左右勁毒既人走埋黎問路 <br />\n問我nathan road點去 開頭都無防範 咁咪用英文同佢講話行番出去條大街就係<br />\n講完之後又話自己趕飛機 想搭e21 咁我咪話 我帶你去搭啦<br />\n帶佢行到出去站 又話自己四點架飛機就飛 心諗你就算搭a車都趕唔到啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我咪建議佢搭的士都probably catch up到 <br />\n之後又叫我幫佢call的 call完幫佢同司機講去機場 <br />\n<br />\n條撚樣開始發作 又話自己身上得百五蚊 心諗你去旅行會唔會遇到咁撚吻呀d時間 同埋又會唔會得百五蚊呀 開頭第一架的士聽到佢話得150都即刻關門走撚左 <br />\n<br />\nOk 就睇下你咩料 我幫佢call第部 今次佢問我可唔可以借d比佢 我都知佢想昆鳩我 我咪用廣東話同佢講 屌你老母搵食行遠d啦 嘩 唔講由自可 講撚完嚇我一跳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條柒頭竟然用地道廣東話回應我 ：<span style=\"color: red;\">「屌你老母 一百幾十都無」<br />\n</span><br />\n即刻火都黎撚埋屌鳩佢 話佢一百幾十都要呃 好心你搵份工啦 因為我講到勁撚大聲 十字路口所有人都聽到 可能佢覺得好柒 即刻走撚左 各位見到真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 起帶佢路個時 佢比左個電話我可以whatsapp佢 又話我好人 唔會忘記我 話下次黎東京要搵佢 之後我試過whatsapp搵唔搵到條柒頭 原來係假既 之後先醒起日本用line同wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70c0603f7379331a127cc9baff3c78094285605","tid":357223,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4f917a196b6245b755c1bace2f9a62e9458d24","tid":357223,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有先例？"},{"pid":"265beabf040f75158f07fde96745b83d4f0ef965","tid":357223,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"條柒頭又係叫eddie 原來08年呃撚到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8390169f4eea30802b1d9a545802d81ff4603d3","tid":357223,"uid":49102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"個case 睇過幾次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bac1cfe1f4f55c64a1b6d9d2d907e887072cc4","tid":357223,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個case 睇過幾次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無睇過丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩一google 完全一撚樣😂"},{"pid":"13ed90f090e3ec46e93b0d087999fa71e169dd46","tid":357223,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"下次影佢相丫麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef0f6f20c78944f1257a3a1790c4a160f73802e","tid":357223,"uid":4304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"又loop<br />\n以為係舊post比人推返上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b9c64e882635c972319918301baac335ba4b1e","tid":357223,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32e59c5f45aea92f1eec1b505ecc4711d655550f","tid":357223,"uid":97250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}